Create django project: django-admin startproject <project name> {.}
Run server: poetry run python manage.py runserver
Create application: poetry run python manage.py startapp <app name>
Create migrations: poetry run python manage.py makemigrations bboard
Run migration: poetry run python manage.py migrate
Run django shell: poetry run python manage.py shell
Close django shell: exit()
Create superuser for admin website: poetry run python manage.py createsuperuser